Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 22:17:03 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 16/16] Gate native reasoning replay by route, API, and model

Persist non-secret inference provenance on assistant turns and replay opaque reasoning only when route, backend, and wire model all match. Convert visible foreign reasoning to portable assistant text and drop opaque-only state across Responses, Messages, and Chat Completions, leaving saved history intact for exact-origin switch-back.
